title: Ripper letter From Hell
description:
By the time she was 16,Molly had already lived to tell a bloodcurdling tale:She was the only survivor of a violent murderer how slaughtered all her friends.Disturbed by her horrific past,she focuses her energies on researching the minds of serial killers.Enrolled in a forensic science program led by famed author and man hunter Martin Kane,She Joins a study group fixated on solving a local campus murder.When the students realize the killers's modus operandi mirrors that of london's legendary Jack the Ripper,Molly's friends once again begin to fall victim around her..
